{"type": "article", "id": 26724, "title": "软奶酪包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-12T06:39:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115047kfKVnLz2rSWFpAXm.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">还有什么比用牛来做奶制品的看板更合适呢？俄罗斯品牌 Fratelli Spirini 委托 Gordost 设计的软奶酪包装就是这么一个让人过目难忘的创意：除了将睁着水汪汪大眼睛的牛直接印上包装，还讨巧地设计了有着立体牛耳和牛角的外包装纸盒。如果你路过货架时一不小心和牛牛对上了视线，很有可能就忍不住把它带回了家。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115045cC5bRh3XVqEBslrv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115046NQvYoDJejpquc9Bx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115046XFNC5DS47ZPlztxK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021150472kcmZ3AaEsdl0USt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}